Lemma forallb_matches_morphism_s : forall ss r r', r =R= r' -> forallb (fun s0 => r ~= s0) ss = forallb (fun s0 => r' ~= s0) ss.
Lemma Star_morphism_s : forall s r r', r =R= r' -> (Star r) ~= s = (Star r') ~= s.
case_eq ((r / a ++ Star r) ~= s); case_eq ((r' / a ++ Star r') ~= s); intros H0 H1; try auto.

specialize(matches_Cat s' s'' (r/a) (Star r) H02 H3).
